<paragraph blockId="99.[151,1437,1082,1418]" pageId="99" pageNumber="100">
<emphasis box="[151,233,1084,1109]" italics="true" pageId="99" pageNumber="100">Leaves</emphasis>
regularly pinnate with 1-veined pinnae, not plicate; rachis 44.5(11.0–87.0) cm long; pinnae 18(6–29) per side of rachis; basal pinna 0.3(0.1–0.5) cm wide, forming an angle of 58(38–77)° with the rachis. 
<emphasis box="[151,319,1160,1186]" italics="true" pageId="99" pageNumber="100">Inflorescences</emphasis>
rachillae 19(4–40).
</paragraph>
